'2017 Daegu Chimac Festival' takes place at Duryu park in Daegu from 19th July till 23th. 'Chimac' is compound word of chicken and beer in South Korea. Last year, 1 million people participated and this festival has been developed and getting famous. Not only this, the festival has a lot of special other events or music show. People who come this festival can feel the energy of youth and make good memories with their friends.
Daegu Chimac Festival is an annual chicken and beer event held at the Duryu Park in July in Daegu, South Korea.
